OOC: Sharpedge has good aim.

:::Jetstorm/Sharpedge/Godfather:::

::Sharpedge gets rammed by Hot Rod and goes into stasis lock.  Godfather's 
wound starts getting mortal and he goes inot stasis lock as well.  jetstorm 
sees this and realizes that althoguh he was not the most loyal of bots, he 
had a duty to keep his comrades alive.  So he transformed to jet mode, picked 
up Sharpedge and Godfather, and flew towards the Iron Fist::
